description:
This is a 125 minute workout called 'Tokyo Night Walking（chill mode）' from the channel Pluto.
The workout falls under Cardio/Walking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Mindful Walk vibe.
The The Mindful Walk vibe means Meditative, story-driven, immersive. This is especially good for When you need fresh air, a change of pace, and mental clarity..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
